title: Return to Masonry
description: 'Alanor was falling. Why was she falling?'	Running for her life, Alanor finds herself transported- literally- into another place; a ruined city, guarded by a stoic, shadow of a man who insists she is the last princess of a forgotten race.	Suddenly thrown into a world much bigger than she realized, Alanor must decide for herself who she is, and make choices she never thought she would.	Can she grow past her uncle's expectations? And should she?
author: Anna Kringle
